{"tid":260131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"佛學黎講，打丁係善業，惡業，定係無記業？","createTime":"2017-05-27T13:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T14:37:41.000Z","uid":26610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"258c80d509fbdc144ee5ed814bdf59caf2884ee0","tid":260131,"uid":26610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n善：打完丁可暫時放低淫慾<br />\n惡： 放縱淫慾<br />\n無記業：無分善惡既日常普通行為"},{"pid":"885966c2045d7159674280b1c31d26adc17a01d7","tid":260131,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"殺一人，救十人<br />\n善？惡？<br />\n<br />\n利伸:反佛撚的耶撚"},{"pid":"141a71f88572f9bea235f6f1adfa0a8f68f47c48","tid":260131,"uid":110286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fba923b0790e0ca4a0cf7affacfb92df82d2051a","tid":260131,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"只要係淫邪 就係貪 就種惡業"},{"pid":"52723e995d910dd41bf3d6722b3371512aef9bfa","tid":260131,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>殺一人，救十人<br />\n善？惡？<br />\n<br />\n利伸:反佛撚的耶撚</blockquote><br />\n咁你地可能要睇吓殺同被殺分別係咪耶&hellip;<br />\n耶殺非耶and非耶殺耶兩個case<br />\n分别係上天定落地獄<br />\nBtw頭先上帝wechat我話殺一人救十人係善<br />\n同埋問依個問題既人係異端，完</blockquote><br />\n雙方既業力所致 整隻腳埋去做咩"},{"pid":"1f00cbedb7e1414cabb352e7e774472e2283bd55","tid":260131,"uid":105907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"惡業同無記業都有 邪淫即惡 打完後昏沈即無記"},{"pid":"41b82858a4384bca8e23a8f4afe8b2c130b427a5","tid":260131,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"唔打j每日都好似生活係地獄咁，別on9啦最多諗住觀音黎j會唔會好d呢？"},{"pid":"8cfe129f1c454e9217db1ffec26993dbcf5259ea","tid":260131,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔打j每日都好似生活係地獄咁，別on9啦最多諗住觀音黎j會唔會好d呢？</blockquote><br />\n好大獲"},{"pid":"d81395cbba52ede86dd53c08a3320a097ced5984","tid":260131,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"想我嬲?"},{"pid":"79334ec608667accf2449856c94648c8c4dbe1a7","tid":260131,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"視情況而定<br />\n<br />\n又窮又廢既人必須要丁，呢種人唔應該繁殖後代，只會製造悲劇。丁多啲丁到死就可以令惡劣基因消失。<br />\n<br />\n淫念重既人要丁多啲，最好丁到腳軟連街都出唔到，減少痴漢強暴女子。慢慢丁到不舉，就可以維護世界和平。<br />\n<br />\n丁完個人應該會輕鬆啲，唔會太執著世事，丁到上癮就只需要執著於丁上面。"},{"pid":"2386198e886c7a8062dc6fd6805516706f63dd9d","tid":260131,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T23:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺一人，救十人<br />\n善？惡？<br />\n<br />\n利伸:反佛撚的耶撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n該死就要死，<br />\n如果十人死亡既業力成熟，殺一人亦會死<br />\n如果十人死亡業力未成熟，不殺一人亦不死"},{"pid":"2944f15e3abd2ca360ae6134ae6cfdc551ba7b77","tid":260131,"uid":48905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/171240_1be9f556762af2ca6ccbba4f4bf79971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F171240_1be9f556762af2ca6ccbba4f4bf79971.jpg&h=36061179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c10f43fef9bee143c8bdda628e49146514a2fd4","tid":260131,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"想我嬲?"}]}